      <div class="about-wrapper">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2 class="about-heading">
            about<br>
            <span class="highlight">the TRAILERs</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/trailer-main.jpg" alt="Mobile Surveillance trailer" class="trailer-photo" />
        </div>

        <div class="video-tech-box">
          <div class="svidia-logo-small"></div>
          <h3 class="video-tech-heading">THE VIDEO TECHNOLOGY</h3>
          <p class="video-tech-text">
            The next-generation S-VIDIA video-based security platform utilizes an unparalleled video compression method that allows for greater quality control.
